%h2 Settle Your Tab
-if(@debts == [])
  Looks like we're all settled up! Either your bill only has one participant, or things just completely equaled out. If you think we're wrong, e-mail 
  %a{:href => "mailto:support@thefinaltab.com"} support@thefinaltab.com
  with a description of your error.
-else
  -@debts.each do |debt|
    -user = debt[0]
    -if(user.picture == nil)
      %img{:src => '/images/defaultprofile.png', :name => user.name}
    -else
      %img{:src => user.picture, :name => user.name}
    -if(user.name == nil)
      ="&nbsp;" + user.email
    -else
      ="&nbsp;" + user.name
    %span.owes &nbsp;&nbsp;owes&nbsp;&nbsp;
    -user = debt[2]
    -if(user.picture == nil)
      %img{:src => '/images/defaultprofile.png', :name => user.name}
    -else
      %img{:src => user.picture, :name => user.name}
    -if(user.name == nil)
      ="&nbsp;" + user.email
    -else
      ="&nbsp;" + user.name
    ="$" + "%.2f" % debt[1].round(2).to_s + "."
    %br
    %br
  .legal-warning WARNING: This information is meant to assist in helping people settle their tabs. All information is provided without warranty and thefinaltab.com is not to be held responsible for any issues arising by the use of information from this website. Decimal places may be off by one cent or more.